Elden Henson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elden_Henson 0 Elden Henson (born Elden Ryan Ratliff; August 30, 1977) is an American actor. He is best known for playing Fulton Reed in The Mighty Ducks trilogy, Foggy Nelson in Daredevil and the wider Marvel Cinematic Universe television series, and Pollux in The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 1 and Part 2.
